文档场景：上市公司企业年报
{
  "document_background": {
    "page_sections": [
      {
        "source_section": "集團首席執行官兼總裁報告",
        "target_section": "Group Chief Executive and President's Report",
        "content_type": "ceo_report",
        "page_range": [
          12,
          16
        ]
      }
    ],
    "roles": [
      {
        "source": "李源祥",
        "target": "Lee Yuen Cheung",
        "role": "Group Chief Executive and President"
      }
    ],
    "terms": [],
    "style_rules": [
      "Use US$ for U.S. dollar amounts.",
      "Keep listed-company annual report disclosure tone formal and publishable.",
      "Do not change numbers, percentages, years, named entities or financial metric values.",
      "For overview narrative, use full financial metric name plus abbreviation when provided.",
      "For financial review and business metrics narrative, use established abbreviations when provided.",
      "Prefer AIA China / AIA Hong Kong / AIA Macau over loose paraphrases when matched."
    ]
  },
  "current_unit": {
    "page_no": 15,
    "unit_id": "p15_g06",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 3,
    "source_text": "過去一個多世紀以來，友邦保險為亞洲客戶的生活帶來正面和持久的影響。我們的社區存在不少環境、社會及管\n治議題，包括氣候變化、環境污染及生活模式相關疾病。隨著疫情大流行持續，突顯了這些問題的複雜性。作為\n客戶和社區的終身夥伴，我們竭盡所能，推動社會邁向更美好、更可持續的未來。",
    "current_translation": "Over more than a century, AIA has made a positive and lasting impact on the lives of our customers across Asia. Our communities face numerous environmental, social and governance issues, including climate change, environmental pollution and lifestyle-related diseases. As the pandemic continues, it has highlighted the complexity of these challenges. As a lifelong partner to our customers and communities, we are committed to doing our part to drive society towards a better and more sustainable future."
  },
  "output_format": {
    "translations": [
      {
        "unit_id": "p15_g06",
        "translation": "<更紧凑译文>"
      }
    ]
  }
}

